Rating: 3
Terrific and easy. I used all chicken broth (no wine) - about 4 cups. I added the broth more gradually than directed (not most all at once), and it was great. I also added about 3/4 cups mushrooms, sliced, which I sauteed with the onions. I imagine you could adapt it to a variety of additions. A good way to sneak in those greens like chard.

